{"tid":336052,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"您估自由行好簡單？","createTime":"2017-07-26T06:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T18:57:15.000Z","uid":88991,"like":7,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e28906b4a378ab7c433c2cfe610f801fec918672","tid":336052,"uid":88991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"小弟ive 仔 3月開始返 full time <br />\n難得夾倒時間，就拎大假同家姐請媽媽去個5日4夜既大阪 京都之旅 係呢到打個小小既遊記同大家分享下旅程既所見所聞<br />\n上年讀書個時同朋友去過一次<br />\n但個時我冇份plan行程 交通個啲<br />\n今次我自己一個搞<br />\n都有啲緊張<br />\n請大家多多支持<br />\n<br />\n講下機票同住宿先<br />\n因為太遲買機票 同埋大家難夾日子<br />\n所以最後只可以買倒 hk express 既機<br />\n每人20kg 既行李 除開3個人 $12000 機票連行李<br />\n<br />\n住方面 今次就book 左一間係(桜川）既民宿 <br />\n4晚3個人都係$3000倒"},{"pid":"a7dc55d21fc45eb7111db330b98f381781d593a6","tid":336052,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"好簡單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f1559aea62c2551e4d33cca3519c64bfd26ca5","tid":336052,"uid":44814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"自由行有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同屋企人都從未跟過團<br />\n<br />\n你買hkexpress買左萬2蚊？係咪假膠黎"},{"pid":"2ae6f2b9641717f1ce8bf4545bf3dfffff3b4bb5","tid":336052,"uid":5547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n所以最後只可以買倒 hk express 既機<br />\n每人20除開3個人 $12000 機票連行李<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當比學費啦<br />\n下次唔好啦？<br />\n你請左好多人坐飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c75be169703e5b52348fab350a24e0374ea40c8","tid":336052,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n所以最後只可以買倒 hk express 既機<br />\n每人20除開3個人 $12000 機票連行李<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當比學費啦<br />\n下次唔好啦？<br />\n你請左好多人坐飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 