:"原來係後面踢櫈個on9仔就係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26686d4db8a8fa7be3bcfd78736839a592dd7334","tid":336052,"uid":44814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n所以最後只可以買倒 hk express 既機<br />\n每人20除開3個人 $12000 機票連行李<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當比學費啦<br />\n下次唔好啦？<br />\n你請左好多人坐飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剛剛早排先買左$1去程機票去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n九月去</blockquote><br />\n如果遲買九成俾人劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遲買仲要買hke<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陰功"},{"pid":"e223aa09634a886034577bb2d7cde02bfe2e1190","tid":336052,"uid":88991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"好快拎埋行李<br />\n就買左(特急....(rapi:t.)既車去大阪<br />\n坐左40分鐘倒<br />\n因為4點先 check得in<br />\n我地鎖左個gip 係nambo 個商場<br />\n就岀發去大阪城<br />\n係森之宮落車 b3岀口 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165356_12991556de32079e6d276cdda0824f4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165356_12991556de32079e6d276cdda0824f4a.jpg&h=583a7461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住求其去左間咖哩餐廳食lunch <br />\n叫左2個一齊share<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165420_6648b35a6433ef6dd4bac62d4712be3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165420_6648b35a6433ef6dd4bac62d4712be3c.jpg&h=54a42830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個原來冇影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普普通通 5分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就去大阪城啦<br />\n上網睇個時都冇為意咁大<br />\n越行越近就越大<br />\n連我呀媽都話誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唔知以前啲人點起<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165516_5624b35ab99b05cf60a9871d34d26719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165516_5624b35ab99b05cf60a9871d34d26719.jpg&h=804d7709&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165526_c04a46f203ea10bba62b65c2a4d6941a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165526_c04a46f203ea10bba62b65c2a4d6941a.jpg&h=febd776d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我仲上埋去大阪城<br />\n不過我唔建議大家比50蚊入去<br />\n冇嘢睇又要行樓梯 <br />\n老人家會好累<br />\n不過頂樓個view 真係幾正<br />\n<br />\n重點提醒大家上落時一定要坐個個火車<br />\n如果唔係都要預行30分鐘<br />\n冬天都ok  夏天真係不了<br />\n最重要係留意班次既時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165605_fbc44c5a7100a6f1fd7b39b6983b715f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165605_fbc44c5a7100a6f1fd7b39b6983b715f.jpg&h=7f260a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09e09fbc74365ecfae43818affa60ebcd2b0f9a2","tid":336052,"uid":131147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好快拎埋行李<br />\n就買左(特急....(rapi:t.)既車去大阪<br />\n坐左40分鐘倒<br />\n因為4點先 check得in<br />\n我地鎖左個gip 係<span style=\"color: red;\">nambo</span> 個商場<br />\n就岀發去大阪城<br />\n係森之宮落車 b3岀口 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165356_12991556de32079e6d276cdda0824f4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165356_12991556de32079e6d276cdda0824f4a.jpg&h=583a7461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住求其去左間咖哩餐廳食lunch <br />\n叫左2個一齊share<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165420_6648b35a6433ef6dd4bac62d4712be3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165420_6648b35a6433ef6dd4bac62d4712be3c.jpg&h=54a42830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個原來冇影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普普通通 5分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就去大阪城啦<br />\n上網睇個時都冇為意咁大<br />\n越行越近就越大<br />\n連我呀媽都話誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唔知以前啲人點起<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165516_5624b35ab99b05cf60a9871d34d26719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165516_5624b35ab99b05cf60a9871d34d26719.jpg&h=804d7709&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165526_c04a46f203ea10bba62b65c2a4d6941a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165526_c04a46f203ea10bba62b65c2a4d6941a.jpg&h=febd776d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我仲上埋去大阪城<br />\n不過我唔建議大家比50蚊入去<br />\n冇嘢睇又要行樓梯 <br />\n老人家會好累<br />\n不過頂樓個view 真係幾正<br />\n<br />\n重點提醒大家上落時一定要坐個個火車<br />\n如果唔係都要預行30分鐘<br />\n冬天都ok  夏天真係不了<br />\n最重要係留意班次既時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/165605_fbc44c5a7100a6f1fd7b39b6983b715f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F165605_fbc44c5a7100a6f1fd7b39b6983b715f.jpg&h=7f260a62&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNamba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534ba445b994857236b196e696507f4088b71e8a","tid":336052,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"講最後一次<br />\n同屋企人去旅行要跟團"},{"pid":"b61318bc5e659ce46527afedad1caf15320d67ed","tid":336052,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-2