 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難用萬二蚊買uo 係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e25cebdca7e24b65a852e2de62026f175215ef5","tid":336052,"uid":34692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"冇錯去旅行真係好難<br />\n坐uo都要4000蚊<br />\n你叫旅遊台串人坐廉航窮撚嗰啲情何以堪"},{"pid":"4a001c142567b4ed39df639c59c2c398c315497e","tid":336052,"uid":4242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"$4000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主係咪買年初一出發d機票？"},{"pid":"8eea217982af96331d047bb81928e29d89e57de9","tid":336052,"uid":40498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錯去旅行真係好難<br />\n坐uo都要4000蚊<br />\n你叫旅遊台串人坐廉航窮撚嗰啲情何以堪</blockquote><br />\n咁有錢應該覺得自由行好易先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54cfd4baaf5f63d5e0cd878901da266c268b52e","tid":336052,"uid":88991,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"多謝大家關心既 但我講既係26/7/2017-30/7/2017既事<br />\n即係我而加人係大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026d74a84feca35f2211d4dcb435e716f6982a75","tid":336052,"uid":13199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"太遲買又熱門日子真係貴好多，如果一定要指定日子去唯有硬食啦。<br />\n最緊要玩得開心就唔怕蝕。"},{"pid":"226ab5567c9c135fde11c5e22212af0baea634ff","tid":336052,"uid":18411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"唔需要驚訝以前D人點起大阪城<br />\n因為依家呢個大阪城係近代重建既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b656cfd8fcf711da39c8fc2ed35bd44eb98e4b1b","tid":336052,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"買hx business 都係5千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a814ae590c77c5ae8f99e05d58e4a7b45fcd968","tid":336052,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝大家關心既 但我講既係26/7/2017-30/7/2017既事<br />\n即係我而加人係大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭ANA一個人都唔洗4000<br />\n你7月仲要係淡季<br />\nAre you joking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebb0ea10ee7f642184c3f049588ece8e606735b","tid":336052,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n所以最後只可以買倒 hk express 既機<br />\n每人20除開3個人 $12000 機票連行李<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當比學費啦<br />\n下次唔好啦？<br />\n你請左好多人坐飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剛剛早排先買左$1去程機票去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n九月去</blockquote><br />\n點樣揾到呢啲優惠？求教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3632b98f3a8d5585007352a1e7f001a309133cb","tid":336052,"uid":84882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講出黎比人笑到面都黃，4千搭廉航"},{"pid":"114f01747adeeb41fb1fa88031ae5ce4dae84d94","tid":336052,"uid":88991,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"好啦 打埋今日個ending 就訓啦<br />\n去完大阪城 就去左心齋橋比屋企人睇下係點既<br />\n因為日後都好多時間係個到<br />\n行左一陣都已經9點<br />\n就去左上次有食既一間鰻魚飯食餐廳食晚飯<br />\n間嘢叫做 本家穴子屋<br />\n裝修非常整齊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/002922_2ebe9726088f290d3c8fa55424927104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F002922_2ebe9726088f290d3c8fa55424927104.jpg&h=14ec7b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食物更加超水準<br />\n我知平時啲人會擺未食之前既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我要引下您班傻仔<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/002903_fe3ff494047a5d3a474ff2d282112435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F002903_fe3ff494047a5d3a474ff2d282112435.jpg&h=5f5591fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問您地怕未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就返左去沖涼訓教啦<br />\n聽日keep going<br />\n晚安各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142b443146b272c236f4a3d756872771281f5bb7","tid":336052,"uid":131147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe34374543c76d240b5d1b183c532dd5684b6785","tid":336052,"uid":14474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  on99"},{"pid":"bb24c73d7fe7745273613dbb567161ddd528c59a","tid":336052,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:40:15.000Z","msg":"好似冇乜野做過咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b530fd9322a1626092e0262e55b