:"2017-07-27T07:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線, 係日本2個人SHARE一個SET? 咪撚認自己香港人丫!</blockquote><br />\n正想講<br />\n真係唔好SHARE餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食嘢未試過唔 share on9"},{"pid":"1060f18882a848f32a1464d5e8be11b81a488dfe","tid":336052,"uid":65406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線, 係日本2個人SHARE一個SET? 咪撚認自己香港人丫!</blockquote><br />\n正想講<br />\n真係唔好SHARE餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食嘢未試過唔 share on9</blockquote><br />\n新香港人?你既思維同大陸人落黎侵略一樣.&quot;要不是...&quot;"},{"pid":"667a8554e76dfb208b4f618cfa291921a24c38e3","tid":336052,"uid":88991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"Day two<br />\n琴晚成1點先訓<br />\n我地今朝都訓到成一點<br />\n諗住試下穿過橙街 去心齋橋食午餐<br />\nOrange street 超正<br />\n沿途有大大小既古十著店<br />\n仲有好多大brand(supreme bape porter x-large carhartt...) <br />\n仲係carhartt買左條bell<br />\n穿到盡頭在行2個街口<br />\n就係心齋橋<br />\n 見倒元祖仔冇人排即刻狗衝啦<br />\n唔夠30分鐘 3個人就飽到跪低<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/154129_09ab4856958ab88d79f13c3fc6a8cdf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F154129_09ab4856958ab88d79f13c3fc6a8cdf0.jpg&h=0e758aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/154131_dbcbf8fddb80a2979f4b7c1f19d822bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F154131_dbcbf8fddb80a2979f4b7c1f19d822bd.jpg&h=a019d509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住而加係難波站唔知咩商場既化妝部 卡住左 已經30分鐘了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/154304_97af9e537fc4bf0b87915def8bfc9e66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F154304_97af9e537fc4bf0b87915def8bfc9e66.jpg&h=512ffa8b&s={